{"word":"Ramoth-Gilead","slug":"ramoth-gilead","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ramoth-Gilead</b> <a href=\"#/H7433\">H7433</a> <br/> Called Ramah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=29'>2Ki 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=6'>2Ch 22:6</a><br/> A city of Gad, and a city of refuge<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=43'>Deu 4:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=20&verse=8'>Jos 20:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=80'>1Ch 6:80</a><br/> One of Solomon's commissaries at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=13'>1Ki 4:13</a><br/> In the possession of the Syrians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=3'>1Ki 22:3</a><br/> Besieged by Israel and Judah; Ahab slain at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=36'>1Ki 22:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=18'>2Ch 18</a><br/> Recovered by Joram; Joram wounded at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=29'>2Ki 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=15'>2Ki 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=6'>2Ch 22:6</a><br/> Elisha anoints Jehu king at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=6'>2Ki 9:6</a>"}]}